    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition and a solid driver for someone who wants something presentable and usable without paying top-tier money for a mint example. It shows normal age-related wear with some cosmetic imperfections and expected use marks inside, but overall it has been maintained better than a typical older car and presents well. The interior is in good, usable shape, and the car should suit a buyer looking for a dependable classic/older vehicle to enjoy as-is while still leaving room for minor cosmetic improvement if desired.",
      "price": 29500.0,
