      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A classic with real vintage charm, this is an honest fair-condition car that offers a great starting point for someone who wants an affordable classic to improve and enjoy over time. It presents well enough to appreciate its old-school style, but it does show its age and should be expected to need some cosmetic and mechanical attention. A solid candidate for an enthusiast who wants character, value, and room to make it their own.",
      "price": 16800.0,
