      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Reliable project or budget runaround with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece and does have its share of wear, but it starts, moves, and could be a great fit for someone handy, needing cheap transport, or looking for a parts/project car. Priced to sell and offered honestly\u2014come take a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid bones and plenty of upside. The engine pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a worthwhile platform for someone who appreciates a car with character. Not cosmetically perfect and it shows its age, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. A good candidate for a budget enthusiast build, weekend tinkering, or a practical get-around with mechanical presence. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6900.0,
